    "en": {
      "title": "A revolutionary victory for Afghanistan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Afghanistan recorded an easy victory of 8 wickets in the match between the Sri Lankan team and the Afghanistan team in the Asian Cup.",
        "The Sri Lankan team batted first in the match and scored 105 runs. The first 3 wickets of the Sri Lankan team were lost for 5 runs.",
        "However, Bhanuka Rajapaksa (38) Chamika Karunaratne (31) took Sri Lanka's innings to 105 runs.",
        "Chasing a target of 106 runs, the Afghanistan team passed the winning target by losing only 2 wickets in 10.1 overs."
      ],
